Usage: setPtnPinUSE [-help] <ptnName> <pinName> <pinUse>

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
<ptnName>                  # Specifies the name of the partition.
                           # (string, required)
<pinName>                  # Specifies name of the pin. (string, required)
<pinUse>                   # The choices represent USE properties that you can
                           # change with this command. (string, required)